  ('dietitian-moex-00581', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'essay', '美國飲食指標之訂定，主要源自 1990 年美國國會通過的國家營養監測
與相關研究法案（NationalNutrition Monitoring andRelated ResearchAct,
NNMRRA）。該法案就食物與健康的關聯性，建構一項國家營養監測的
架構，可作為社區膳食營養評估之依據。請詳述此架構及其中五項重要
資料組成所代表之意義。（15分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:51+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "6300cf2ce819", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112030", "c": "101", "s": "0105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00582', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-112-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'essay', '為改善國人營養狀況，政府正積極推廣全穀及未精製雜糧的攝取。健康
